                <head>314. Telegram 962 from Geneva<note n="1" type="source" xml:id="d314fn1"
                        >Source: Department of State, Central Files, 611.93/10–2655. Official Use
                        Only; Priority.</note>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>Geneva</placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1955-10-26"
                            >October 26, 1955, 10 a.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <pb facs="d314-1" n="1" type="facsimile" xml:id="d314-1"/>
                <p>962. From <persName corresp="#p_JUA_1">Johnson</persName>.</p>
                <p>Would appreciate some reply my 871 prior to tomorrow’s WPP Meeting.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_GFC_1">
                            <hi rend="strong">Gowen</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
